body:
15 Questions, 15 Mutuals

I was tagged by the lovely @abundantlyabundant and @waitingfortwilight

Are you named after anyone? I wish I had some cool story behind my name but I’m not unfortunately. Though half of my first name is Welsh so that’s a fun fact 😂

When was the last time you cried? Reading Kate’s Private Universe IV. Thanks for that 😂😭

Do you have any kids? I don’t but I want them eventually

Do you use sarcasm a lot? I use sarcasm more than I use any other form of the English language

What’s the first thing you notice about people? Their hair? But when they’re up close their eyes. I’m fascinated by the millions of different eyes there are in the world 👀

What’s your eye colour? I have blue eyes with a hint of grey in them

Scary movie or happy ending? Happy ending ALWAYS. I hate scary movies so much

Any special talents? Making it look like I’m paying attention in class when I’m really writing fics

Where were you born? Ooh fun one!!! My dad was a paramedic in the army so I was born in Paderborn, Germany!! Though I moved to the U.K. when I was 6 months old so I can’t speak more than what I learnt at uni 🤷🏻‍♀️

Any hobbies? Besides writing, photography and listening to music 🎵📸

Do you have pets? I have toy poodle called Molly and my cat called Mickey 🐩🐈

Do you play sports? Honey that’s the funniest question I’ve ever read. Heck no!

How tall are you? I’m 5’6” I think. Haven’t measured myself in a hot minute

Favourite subject? I’m not at school anymore but when I was I had two. Maths and history

Dream job? Having my own event planning company! Or touring with musicians

I tag (and sorry if you’ve already been tagged): @yes-daddy-i-willl @for-fucks-sake-h @tiostyles @always-jackedup @writingsfromlee @emotionally-imbruised @biteharrysthigh @harrygivenchy @betchyharry

I know that isn’t 15 but you’ll cope 😂😂

happy 2 years 🎉

it was actually yesterday but since i didn’t sleep yet i came here to thank every single people who follows my tumblr, likes and reblogs my layout posts!

doing this is my fav hobby and i really hope that y’all appreciate and like as much as i do! i know i’m not as active as i used to (blame uni for that one), but just hold tight, i always come back when i can and when we get hontent.

thank you for all the support until today, the best thing for me is seeing that y’all like what i’m doing and using it! besides, obviously, every compliment, every like and reblog, every follow!

and btw, 2 years and almost 9k! i couldn’t be more happy 🥰

thank you 💛

kissy, ginni xx
